---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="carles.sh | About"
  description="About Carles, Master's Student in Informatics Engineering and AI Researcher at GREIA."
>
  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="about-hero glass-panel">
      <div class="intro-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Hi there</p>
        <h1>I'm Carles.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          I am doing a Master's in Informatics Engineering and helping with AI research at
          <a class="muted-link" href="https://greia.udl.cat/">GREIA</a>. I mostly try to build things that are useful,
          understandable, and not held together only by hope.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most of my code is Python and C/C++. I like data science, machine learning, and cybersecurity, especially when
          there is an actual problem to solve and not just a fancy name for a folder full of scripts.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="portrait-card content-card" aria-label="Profile summary">
        <img src="https://github.com/carless7.png" alt="Carles GitHub profile image" loading="lazy" />
        <div>
          <strong>Carles</strong>
          <span>Informatics Engineering | AI Research | GREIA</span>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="about-grid">
      <article class="text-window glass-panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">What I do</p>
        <h2>Technical work, kept separate from the personal stuff.</h2>
        <p>
          My working zone is practical software and applied research. I like tools that make a hard problem easier to
          inspect: data pipelines, model experiments, low-level performance decisions, and systems that do not hide their
          trade-offs.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am currently working on a music recommendation project inside the
          <a class="muted-link" href="https://github.com/orgs/spotifai-tfg">SpotifAI</a> organization.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="text-window glass-panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Who I am</p>
        <h2>Outside the editor.</h2>
        <p>
          I listen to a lot of music, which explains why music projects keep finding their way into my technical work.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also support FC Barcelona, which is character-building whether I asked for it or not.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-strip glass-panel">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Connect with me</p>
        <h2>One useful link for now.</h2>
      </div>
      <a class="aqua-button green" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/carles-sanchez">LinkedIn</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) 300px;
    gap: clamp(20px, 4vw, 38px);
    align-items: center;
    padding: clamp(22px, 4vw, 44px);
  }

  .intro-copy p:not(.eyebrow) {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .portrait-card {
    padding: 14px;
  }

  .portrait-card img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    border-radius: 22px;
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8),
      0 10px 22px rgba(0, 55, 100, 0.22);
  }

  .portrait-card div {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .portrait-card strong,
  .portrait-card span {
    display: block;
  }

  .portrait-card strong {
    color: var(--ink-strong);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .portrait-card span {
    margin-top: 4px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .text-window {
    padding: clamp(18px, 3vw, 30px);
  }

  .contact-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: clamp(18px, 3vw, 28px);
  }

  .contact-strip h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-hero,
    .about-grid,
    .contact-strip {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .portrait-card {
      max-width: 340px;
    }
  }
</style>
